            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Hd1e108">Rubrica 2</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De fidelitate et fide et infidelitate seu perfidia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e114"> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/>De fide seu fidelitate / et de 
               <lb ed="#P" n="10"/>infidelitate / seu perfidia.
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/>capitulum ii
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P" n="12"/><ref>Salomon in prouerb. ca. xiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e127">legatus fide
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="13"/>lis sanitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/><ref>Ibidem. xx. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e135">virum fidelem quis inueniet</quote>
               <lb ed="#P" n="15"/><ref>Ibidem xxviii. ca.</ref> <quote>Vir fidelis multum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="16"/>laudabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#P" n="17"/><ref>Aristoteles rethoricorum. ca. primo. libro. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e148">die
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/>rare iniustum facere est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#P" n="19"/><ref>Salustius iniugurtino.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e158">Expertus sum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="20"/>miseris parum fideu esse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/><ref>Oratius in epistolis libro. ii. epistola. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="22"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e168">Multa fidem promissa levant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#P" n="23"/><ref>Tullius de officiis libro. primo. ca. x.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e178">Fun
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="24"/>damentum iustitie est fides. i. conuentorum
               <lb ed="#P" n="25"/>constantia / et veritas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#P" n="26"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. xiiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e188">Nec promissa servanda 
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/>sunt / eaque sunt his / quibus promiseris in
               <lb ed="#P" n="28"/>utilia / nec si plus tibi ea noceant 
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/>quam illi prosint cui quid promiseris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/><ref>Ibidem libro. ii. ca. xxxviiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e200">Nulla res 
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/>vehementius rem publicam continet quam fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#P" n="32"/><ref>Ibidem libro. iii. ca. xxii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e211">Quod ita inuratum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="33"/>est ut mens conciperet id fieri opor
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="34"/>tere / id seruandum est quod aliter <s>aliter</s> si 
               <lb ed="#P" n="35"/>non fecerit nullum secunandum est periurium</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/><ref>Idem de amicitia.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e223">in vita tirannorum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="37"/>Nulla fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e229">
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/><ref>Idem rethoricorum artis verteris libro. primo. ca.
               <lb ed="#P" n="39"/>xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e231">animus sine fide stabilis amicis 
               <lb ed="#P" n="40"/>esse non potest. Qui sepe nos numero fefelle
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="41"/>runt per fidem eorum errori fidem habere non 
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/>debemus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/><ref>Ouidius de arte amandi libro. primo.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="44"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e245">Reddite depositum pietas sua federa seruet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/><ref>Idem de fastis libro. iii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e253">Tarda verit dictis difficilisque fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e265">
               <lb ed="#P" n="47"/><ref>Idem de ponto libro. v. sti. iiii. et fi: epistola. x.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e267">Quis labor est puram non temerare fidem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#P" n="49"/><ref>Seneca tragediarum in agamenone. ca. viii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e278">pretio parata vincitur pretio fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/><ref>Idem de moribus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e280">priusquem promictas deliberes
               <lb ed="#P" n="52"/>et eum promiseris facies.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e294">
               <lb ed="#P" n="53"/><ref>Idem in proverbiis</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e296">Etiam peccato recte prestatur 
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/>fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e302">
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><ref>Luchanus libro. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e306">Nulla fides regni <sic>so</sic>
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/>sociis omnis quem potestas Impatiens consortis erit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/><ref>Ibidem libro. x. et fi:</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e314">Nulla fides pietasque viris qui castra se
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="59"/>quuntur. Venalesque manus ibi fas ubi maxi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="60"/>ma merces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e324">
               <lb ed="#P" n="61"/><ref>Iuuenalis libro. primo. satura. iii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="62"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e328">Quantum quisque sua nummorum seruat in archa
               <lb ed="#P" n="63"/>Tantum habet et fidei.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e335">
               <lb ed="#P" n="64"/><ref>Lex. ff. ti. depac. l. i. in prin.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e339">Quid tam
               <lb ed="#P" n="65"/>congruum est fidei humane qued ea que intur 
               <lb ed="#P" n="66"/>eos placuerunt seruare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e347">
               <pb ed="#P" n="46-v"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="1"/><ref>ibidem. ti. deconsti. pecu. l i. in prin.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e349">Graue 
               <lb ed="#P" n="2"/>est fidem fallere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e355">
               <lb ed="#P" n="3"/><ref>Ibidem. ti. ma. lo si fidum iussor. ยง. quendam</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="4"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e357">Bone fidei non congruit / de inuris ap
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="5"/>picibus disputare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e365">
               <lb ed="#P" n="6"/><ref>Ibidem. ti: loca. et condue. l. cum venditor</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="7"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e369">bona fides exigit ut id quod conuenit 
               <lb ed="#P" n="8"/>fiat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e375">
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/><ref>Lex. c. de non. nume. pec. l. generaliter</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e377">ni
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="10"/>mis indignum esse vidicamus autem quod 
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/>quisque sua voce dilucide protestatus est
               <lb ed="#P" n="12"/>id in eundem casum in firmare testimonio
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="13"/>que proprio resistere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e389">
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/><ref>Martialis chocus libro undique suscepto
               <lb ed="#P" n="15"/>ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e393">Sponsio res nova sponsor ver
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="16"/>satilis aura. Noli spondenti fidere 
               <lb ed="#P" n="17"/>digne nimis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e402">
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e404">Magna quidem dare promit
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="19"/>tere parva decorum est. Te facere 
               <lb ed="#P" n="20"/>et gloria nulla tibi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e412">
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e414">Inscrutabilis est male
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="22"/>fidei semper abissus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e420">
               <lb ed="#P" n="23"/><ref>Vegotuis de re militari. libro. iii. ca.
               <lb ed="#P" n="24"/>viiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e424">aduersis rebus rarior est fi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="25"/>des ubi nutare cepit qui copiosus 
               <lb ed="#P" n="26"/>aduenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e432">
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/><ref>Auctor libri. de formula honeste vite.
               <lb ed="#P" n="28"/>ca. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e436">Cum consideratione promitte. et 
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/>plenius quam promiseris praesta.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e444">
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/><ref>Ibidem</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e446">nichil tibi intersit an affirmes 
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/>an iures de religione ac fide agi 
                 <lb ed="#P" n="32"/>scias ubicumque de veritate tractatur 
               <lb ed="#P" n="33"/>Si contigerit fidelitatem mendacio redimi
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="34"/>non mentieris sed potius excusaberis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e456">
               <lb ed="#P" n="35"/><ref>Ambrosus de officiis libro. primo. ca. xxviii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e460">liquet etiam in bello fidem et iustitiam obser
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="37"/>vari oportere fundamentum iustitie 
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/>est fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e469">
               <lb ed="#P" n="39"/><ref>Ibidem libro. ii. ca. vi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e471">auaritia perfidie vi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="40"/>cina est</quote>
               <lb ed="#P" n="41"/><ref>Ibidem libro. iii. et fi. ca. xii.</ref> <quote>unusquisque 
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/>nichil promittat in honestum / at si pro
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/>miserit tolerabilius est promissum non 
               <lb ed="#P" n="44"/>facere quam facere quod turbe sit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e490">
               OMITTED
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e502">
               OMITTED
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e512">
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/><ref>Isidorus in sinonima soliloquiorum libro. ii.
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/>ca. xxxv.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e516">fac bonum quod spopondisti ad. 
               <lb ed="#P" n="47"/>sis in verbis facilis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e524">
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/><ref>Ibidem xxxvi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e526">in malis promissis rescin
               <lb ed="#P" n="49"/>de fidem / impia est promissio / quae sedere 
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/>adipletur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e532">
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/><ref>Cato. ca. primo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e536">datum serua</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e541">
               <lb ed="#P" n="52"/><ref>Idem. ca. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="53"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e545">Rem tibi promissam certam promictere noli
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/>Rara fides ideo quia. multi multa loquuntur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e551">
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><ref>Versificator fabularum exopi fabula. xxxi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e555">Expedit infido non interare fidem. 
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/>Que dedit in fidus mala venena puto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e563">
               OMITTED
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e575">
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/><ref>Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria parte primo.
               <lb ed="#P" n="59"/>ca. .</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e579">Actura fidei notat inconstantia 
               <lb ed="#P" n="60"/>mentis. Palperat in vario pectore ra
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="61"/>ra fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e587">
               <lb ed="#P" n="62"/><ref>Iacobus beneuetanus. in poetria ca.
               <lb ed="#P" n="63"/>xviiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e591">Si tibi quod pro missum fuerit tibi 
                 sus<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="64"/>cipe raptum. Mens a proposito nam 
                 resi<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="65"/>lire potest.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e599">
               <pb ed="#P" n="47-r"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="1"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. xx.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e601">Qui spondet multa spon
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="2"/>dere pauca solet. Quod dare nolu
               <lb ed="#P" n="3"/>eris nulli spondebis amice. Dedecet 
               <lb ed="#P" n="4"/>hoc euentos praecipueque bonos. Cum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="5"/>spondes aliquid manus ilico verba se
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="6"/>quatur / Auget enim meritum qui cito 
               <lb ed="#P" n="7"/>soluit idem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e616">
               <lb ed="#P" n="8"/><ref>Auctor libri de moribus medicorum. ca.
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/>iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e620">Cum dolet infirmus promittit 
               <lb ed="#P" n="10"/>premia multa. Cessat promissum cum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/>dolor ipse cadit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-d1e628">
               <lb ed="#P" n="12"/><ref>Ricardus Iudex venusinus libro 
               <lb ed="#P" n="13"/>de pertractatatione nuptiarum. ca. xxxvii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24063-Qd1e632">Quis bonus absque fide.
               <lb ed="#P" n="15"/>Est homo vas vacuum deficiente fide
               <lb ed="#P" n="16"/>virtutis alias frustra conaris habere
               <lb ed="#P" n="17"/>Si virtus fidei deficit ipsa tibi.</quote>
            </p>
